---
title: Garlic-Ginger Glazed Beef with Green Beans and Rice
description: No need for take out! We make our own sweet and savory teriyaki sauce to coat our juicy beef and crisp green beans. Top it off with some crispy shallots. You won't be able to grab your chopsticks fast enough!
